.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
City: venice, san-francisco
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, dancer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
3. the person traveling to venice is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| City    | san-francisco | venice     |
| Job     | dancer | accountant |
| Sport   | skiing | sailing    |

 #################################

 
