.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-13::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, nectarine
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, september
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Beverage      | tea        | soy-milk  |
| Food          | cranberry  | nectarine |
| Birthday   | september | march   |

